commit.message: Move the test script to root and make sure it's executable

Provide a base face for the error faces too

Release 2.1.4.

Inherit all rainbow-delimiters faces from a base face

With a common base face it is possible for a user to set a face
attribute to all rainbow-delimiter faces by manipulating just
rainbow-delimiters-base-face.
syntax-begin-function is obsolete, so test for its existence

Use skip-syntax-forward instead of re-search-forward

Time needed to do 1000 fontifications of rainbow-delimiters.el:
Before: 3.01 s
After: 2.25 s

Make it clear that global-rainbow-delimiters-mode is no more

Fixes #13

Deprecate rainbow-delimiters-delimiter-blacklist.

rainbow-delimiters-pick-face-function offers a superset of its
functionality.
Allow the user to customize the way faces are picked.
Move the usage instructions from installation to commentary.
Move installation instructions before the commentary.
